    <string name="settings_ocr_intro">Pick the OCR engine for the text type:\n• Auto / Japanese / Korean / Chinese / Latin: Google ML Kit on-device (free, offline). \"Auto\" picks the model by detecting Hangul / kana; pinning a specific language slightly improves accuracy.\n• PaddleOCR: on-device multilingual; better on complex layouts. First use downloads ~20MB models. (Korean dict not bundled — use ML Kit or cloud for Korean.)\n• Baidu / Tencent Cloud: cloud OCR with API key (pay-as-you-go); pick Korean / Japanese etc. under \"Recognition language\" as a fallback.</string>
